item.title: Set Presentation Source Locking Behavior API for Python Apps
item.description: Aspose.Slides for Python via .NET 22.6 win64 Download  Support Forum  File Details Downloads: 1 File Size: 54.14MB Date Added: 8/7/2022 Release Noteshttps://releases.aspose.com/slides/python-net/release-notes/2022/aspose-slides-for-python-net-22-6-release-notes/ DescriptionPresentation Manipulation Python API File Details Updated Presentation Source Locking Behavior The obsolete PresentationLockingBehavior LOAD_AND_RELEASE_LEGACY_TEMPORARY_DEFAULT ENUM member has been removed. LOAD_AND_RELEASE is the default presentation locking behavior now. This default setting locks the source only for the time of IPresentation constructor execution.
